➤ Rapture Truth Website - https://www.rapturetruth.com
➤ Will You Be Left Behind? - https://www.rapturetruth.com/resources/articles/id/1880/will-you-be-left-behind

Many religions in addition to Christianity teach about a great day when an all powerful being will bring a kind of judgment to the world. The Bible talks about The Day of the Lord. What is this day? Is it  important for us to study it? How does the "left behind" scenario differ? Please join us for this episode.
